snippet.title: Hyper X Cloud II - Up To Date Review (2018)
snippet.description:
I show you what the HyperX Cloud II has to offer in 2018 that most other headphones don't. I tell you why this is the best gaming headset on the market. 

HyperX Cloud II on Amazon: https://amzn.to/2HB2lzB

I hope you enjoyed my HyperX Cloud II Review!

What gaming headset are you using? What do you LOVE or HATE about it? I'm looking forward to your answer, I used to own a Logitech G930 and it was getting a bit dated and wasn't as comfortable as these.
